---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About PlayerStall | 30+ Years of Custom Wood Sports Lockers"
	description="Discover the PlayerStall story—30+ years of Canadian craftsmanship, lifetime guarantee, and premium custom wood sports lockers for collegiate and professional teams."
>
	<div class="about-page">
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="hero" id="hero">
			<div class="playoff-text">ABOUT US</div>
			<div class="hero-content">
				<p class="hero-subtitle">Since 1994 • Made in Canada • Serving North America</p>
				<h1 class="hero-title">30+ Years of Craftsmanship</h1>
				<p class="hero-text">PlayerStall is a multigenerational family business laser-focused on building the highest quality custom wood sports lockers. We've partnered with collegiate powerhouses, pro organizations, and elite high schools to transform their locker rooms into culture hubs.</p>
				<div class="hero-buttons">
					<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Free Consultation</a>
					<a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline">Explore Products</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-image">
				<img src="https://topscorer.qodeinteractive.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/h3-rev-img-2.png" alt="About PlayerStall" />
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="story-section" id="story">
			<div class="container story-grid">
				<div class="story-copy">
					<h2>Our Story</h2>
					<p class="lead">
						For over three decades we've remained the trusted name in custom wood sports lockers. While others diversify, we double
						down on one craft—premium wood lockers that elevate every locker room they inhabit.
					</p>
					<p>
						The PlayerStall difference comes from our relentless focus on quality, value, and service. We obsess over joinery,
						ventilation, electrical integration, and modular construction so that you get a locker that looks elite on day one
						and still turns heads fifteen seasons later.
					</p>
					<p>
						We don’t produce metal, plastic, or generic storage. We build wood sports lockers—only wood—and we’ve perfected every
						cut, finish, and install detail to prove it.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="story-visual">
					<div class="visual-card">
						<p>30+ Years</p>
						<h3>Canadian Built. North America Proud.</h3>
						<span>Premium 3/4" birch • Modular repair • Pro-level finishing</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="values-section" id="values">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>What Sets PlayerStall Apart</h2>
				<div class="values-grid">
					{[
						{
							title: '30+ Years Experience',
							copy:
								"Trends fade. Craftsmanship lasts. We’ve delivered elite locker rooms through every generation of uniforms, cleats, and coaching staffs."
						},
						{
							title: 'Family Business',
							copy:
								"Your project has our family name on it. That accountability shapes every conversation, CAD drawing, and delivery."
						},
						{
							title: 'Made in Canada',
							copy:
								"100% manufactured on North American soil with responsibly sourced premium birch. No shortcuts, no mystery materials."
						},
						{
							title: 'Exclusive Wood Focus',
							copy:
								"We’ve said no to metal so we can say yes to excellence. Specialization gives you deeper expertise, cleaner installs, and smarter solutions."
						},
						{
							title: 'Lifetime Guarantee',
							copy:
								"Our modular design means we can service, repair, or replace individual components without touching the rest of your build."
						},
						{
							title: 'Free Custom Design',
							copy:
								"Every engagement starts with a complimentary design consultation, locker room layout, and spec package tailored to your space."
						}
					].map((value) => (
						<div class="value-card">
							<h3>{value.title}</h3>
							<p>{value.copy}</p>
						</div>
					))}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="process-section" id="process">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<p class="eyebrow">How We Deliver</p>
					<h2>From Idea to Install in Five Steps</h2>
					<p class="lead">
						Our turnkey process removes friction so you can focus on culture, recruiting, and performance.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="process-grid">
					{[
						{
							step: '01',
							title: 'Free Consultation',
							copy:
								"We start with a detailed discovery covering roster size, equipment profile, branding goals, and timeline."
						},
						{
							step: '02',
							title: 'Custom Design',
							copy:
								"Our design studio delivers layouts, elevations, and specs dialed into your exact square footage and workflow."
						},
						{
							step: '03',
							title: 'Manufacturing',
							copy:
								"Every locker is precision-built in Canada with premium 3/4\" birch, pro-grade hardware, and meticulous finishing."
						},
						{
							step: '04',
							title: 'Installation Support',
							copy:
								"We ship complete install packs, labeled components, and offer on-call support or on-site coordination for larger builds."
						},
						{
							step: '05',
							title: 'Lifetime Support',
							copy:
								"Need a replacement panel, extra grommets, or wire management upgrade? We’re here long after install day."
						}
					].map((item) => (
						<div class="process-card">
							<span class="step-number">{item.step}</span>
							<h3>{item.title}</h3>
							<p>{item.copy}</p>
						</div>
					))}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="guarantee-section" id="guarantee">
			<div class="container guarantee-grid">
				<div class="guarantee-copy">
					<p class="eyebrow">Lifetime Guarantee</p>
					<h2>We Don’t Stop Until You’re 100% Satisfied</h2>
					<p class="lead">
						Our modular approach allows us to service individual components—shelf, seat, face frame—without dismantling your entire locker.
					</p>
					<div class="guarantee-points">
						<div>
							<h4>What’s Covered</h4>
							<ul>
								<li>Construction defects</li>
								<li>Material failures</li>
								<li>Workmanship issues</li>
								<li>Replacement part availability</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4>Modular Advantage</h4>
							<p>
								Damaged component? We ship replacements cut to spec so your facilities team swaps parts in hours, not weeks.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4>Our Commitment</h4>
							<p>
								Three decades in, our promise is simple: if something isn’t right, we fix it fast. That’s how we earn repeat business and
								referrals.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="guarantee-visual">
					<div class="guarantee-card">
						<h3>Built for Decades</h3>
						<p>15+ year installs that still look day-one fresh.</p>
						<span>1 (888) 58-STALL • info@customsportslockers.com</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="wood-section">
			<div class="container wood-grid">
				<div class="wood-copy">
					<p class="eyebrow">Why Wood Wins</p>
					<h2>Wood Lockers Outperform Metal</h2>
					<p class="lead">
						We’ve built with every material imaginable. Wood is the only one that delivers durability, prestige, and limitless customization.
					</p>
					<div class="wood-points">
						<div class="wood-card">
							<h4>Durability That Lasts</h4>
							<p>Properly sealed birch resists dents, rust, and fatigue. Metal can’t claim the same after six seasons of game day use.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="wood-card">
							<h4>Prestige & Culture</h4>
							<p>Wood turns a storage room into a recruiting asset. LED halos, nameplates, and finishes tie directly into your brand.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="wood-card">
							<h4>Natural Comfort</h4>
							<p>Warm surfaces, softer acoustics, and odor control give athletes a space they actually want to occupy.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="wood-card">
							<h4>Unlimited Customization</h4>
							<p>Integrate vents, USB/120V, helmet cradles, shoe drawers, and media tech without being confined to prefab metal molds.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="wood-visual">
					<img
						src="/images/Athletic-Lockers-Stadium.jpg"
						alt="PlayerStall custom wood sports lockers"
						loading="lazy"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="cta-section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="cta-card">
					<p class="eyebrow">Ready to build something legendary?</p>
					<h2>Book Your Free Custom Design Consultation</h2>
					<p>
						Walk away with a tailored locker room concept, pricing options across all five PlayerStall tiers, and a clear install plan.
					</p>
					<div class="cta-actions">
						<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Start the Conversation</a>
						<a href="/gallery" class="btn btn-outline btn-large">See Recent Installs</a>
					</div>
					<span class="cta-note">Prefer to talk now? Call 1 (888) 58-STALL.</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	:root {
		--dark-bg: #050505;
		--panel-bg: #111;
		--text-light: #f5f5f5;
		--text-muted: #9da0a8;
		--accent: #fe5900;
		--accent-soft: rgba(254, 89, 0, 0.15);
	}

	.about-page {
		background: #f7f7f7;
		color: #0d0d0d;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1300px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 20px;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: #8c8c8c;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.section-header {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 760px;
		margin: 0 auto 3rem;
	}

	.section-header h2 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
		color: #0d0d0d;
	}

	.section-header .lead {
		color: #666666;
	}

	/* Hero Section */
	.hero {
		position: relative;
		height: 800px;
		background: #f7f7f7;
		overflow: hidden;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: flex-start;
		padding-left: 10%;
		margin-top: 0;
	}

	.playoff-text {
		position: absolute;
		font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
		font-size: 350px;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: rgba(13, 13, 13, 0.03);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: -3px;
		z-index: 1;
		top: 50%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.hero-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 10;
		max-width: 600px;
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		font-family: 'Yantramanav', sans-serif;
		font-size: 13px;
		color: #8c8c8c;
		letter-spacing: 0.3em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.hero-title {
		font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
		font-size: 80px;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #0d0d0d;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		line-height: 80px;
		margin-bottom: 30px;
	}

	.hero-text {
		font-family: 'Yantramanav', sans-serif;
		font-size: 20px;
		color: #666666;
		line-height: 30px;
		margin-bottom: 40px;
	}

	.hero-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 20px;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 15px 40px;
		text-decoration: none;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		font-size: 20px;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: #fe5900;
		color: #ffffff;
		border: 2px solid #fe5900;
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		background: #e04d00;
		border-color: #e04d00;
	}

	.btn-outline {
		background: transparent;
		color: #0d0d0d;
		border: 2px solid #bfbfbf;
	}

	.btn-outline:hover {
		border-color: #0d0d0d;
		color: #0d0d0d;
	}

	.btn-large {
		padding: 1.25rem 3rem;
	}

	.hero-image {
		position: absolute;
		right: 0;
		top: 50%;
		transform: translateY(-50%);
		z-index: 5;
	}

	.hero-image img {
		max-width: 810px;
		height: auto;
	}

	.story-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: #ffffff;
	}

	.story-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.story-copy h2 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.story-copy .lead {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.story-copy p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.story-visual {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.visual-card {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111, #1f1f1f);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		border-radius: 24px;
		padding: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	}

	.visual-card p {
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--accent);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.visual-card h3 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.visual-card span {
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.values-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: #f7f7f7;
	}

	.values-section h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.values-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.value-card {
		background: #0f0f0f;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 16px;
		box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
	}

	.value-card h3 {
		margin-top: 0;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	.value-card p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.process-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: #ffffff;
	}

	.process-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.process-card {
		background: #000;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 16px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		position: relative;
		min-height: 220px;
	}

	.step-number {
		position: absolute;
		top: 1.5rem;
		right: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.3rem;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.process-card h3 {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	.process-card p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.guarantee-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: #f7f7f7;
	}

	.guarantee-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.guarantee-copy h2 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.guarantee-points {
		display: grid;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.guarantee-points h4 {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.guarantee-points p,
	.guarantee-points li {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.guarantee-points ul {
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.guarantee-visual {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.guarantee-card {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, #101010, #1a1a1a);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
		border-radius: 24px;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		text-align: center;
		box-shadow: 0 25px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
	}

	.guarantee-card h3 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.guarantee-card p {
		color: var(--accent);
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.guarantee-card span {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.wood-section {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: #ffffff;
	}

	.wood-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.wood-copy h2 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.wood-copy .lead {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.wood-points {
		display: grid;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.wood-card {
		background: #111;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}

	.wood-card h4 {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.wood-card p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.wood-visual img {
		width: 100%;
		border-radius: 24px;
		box-shadow: 0 35px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}

	.cta-section {
		padding: 6rem 0;
		background: #0d0d0d;
		text-align: center;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.cta-card {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
		padding: 3rem;
		border-radius: 24px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	}

	.cta-card h2 {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
		margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
	}

	.cta-card p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.cta-actions {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	.cta-note {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.hero-title {
			font-size: 48px;
			line-height: 1.2;
		}

		.hero-image {
			display: none;
		}

		.playoff-text {
			font-size: 150px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.container {
			padding: 0 1.25rem;
		}

		.hero {
			height: 600px;
			padding-left: 20px;
		}

		.hero-title {
			font-size: 36px;
			line-height: 1.2;
		}

		.hero-text {
			font-size: 16px;
		}

		.hero-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.playoff-text {
			font-size: 100px;
		}

		.section-header h2,
		.story-copy h2,
		.values-section h2,
		.guarantee-copy h2,
		.wood-copy h2 {
			font-size: 2.25rem;
		}

		.visual-card {
			padding: 2rem;
		}

		.process-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.cta-actions {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}
</style>

